       15.3  CCCCoooonnnnttttrrrroooolllllllliiiinnnngggg IIIIccccoooonnnn AAAAppppppppeeeeaaaarrrraaaannnncccceeee aaaannnndddd BBBBeeeehhhhaaaavvvviiiioooorrrr

       MWM offers a number of resources to control the appearance    |
       and behavior of icons.  Among these are resources that
